         <abstract id="aspace_74c98fb9ea8210a209627778276b440d">Notes and papers from Riemer's years at the Yale Divinity School (1915-1917) provide insight into the curriculum and teaching methods at YDS during the first part of the twentieth century. Reinhold Riemer was a Yale Divinity School graduate, Moravian minister, and President of the Moravian College for Women.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname source="local">
               <part>Riemer, Reinhold, 1889-1955</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
